name: Jesus Never Fails - 11x17 Christian Poster
description:
Jesus Never Fails.
Never has. Never will. Period.
11x17 Poster
 
We want Paper Movement posters to look fantastic and last a long time. All of our posters are printed on high quality, heavyweight paper stock. 
This poster is printed on 80lb Gloss Cover Weight Paper.
 
This item ships rolled in a sturdy mailing tube.

$1 from the sale of this poster goes towards rescuing Untouchable Children.
